+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+++ Files organization							+++
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
--{root}		- Workspace directory.
    +--ChibiOS/		- ChibiOS-RT directory (optional).
    +--build_system/	- Build system directory.
    |	+--templates/	- Templates directory.
    |	+--README	- This file.
    |	+--build.sh	- Build system's shell scrypt file.
    +--projects/	- Projects directory (Build system create it).
    +--build.sh		- Soft link to build system's scrypt file (Build system create it).


+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+++ How to use the build system						+++
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
1. Setting up the work space.
    $mkdir workspace; cd workspace

2. Download the ChibiOS build system.
    $git clone https://github.com/LaszloTamas/ChibiOS_build_system.git
    $cd ChibiOS_build_system

4. Install build system.
    $./build.sh install			- Follow the build system's steps.

5. Create a new project
    $./build.sh create			- Follow the build system's steps.


